- Click on three dots appearing on the pop-up
- A remove option will appear click on remove and the app will get removed successfully.

Copy the URL and open in a new tab - https://XXXXXXXXXXXX/Office365Timesheet/lists/manager%20of%20employee

It will show 2 records and then delete one of them and save the list
Make sure do not make any changes else it will affect the production data.

Questions/ Issue: How to remove timesheet app from office 365?
Answer /Steps to Resolve:
To remove the app from the site please follow the below steps:-
Login to sharepoint using Administrator account
Click on setting icon
Go to contents
Locate office 365 timesheet app
Click the 3 dots on office 365 app – a popup will appear
Click on three dots appearing on the pop-up
A remove option will appear click on remove and the app will get removed successfully.

Questions/ Issue: Who can download timesheet.?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: Only the administrator of sharepoint can download the app.

Questions/ Issue: Can manager see reports?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: only the associated manager of the empoyee can see the employee report and The administrator of the add-in can see all the employee report.

Questions/ Issue: Can we create multiple admin in timesheet app?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: Yes, there can be more than one admin.

Questions/ Issue: I am the employee and I am the manager as well, want to submit my timesheet and aprove myself can it is possible in timesheet app?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: In pro version of timesheet app has the functionality of super manager by this manager can fill his timesheet and approve his own timesheet.

Questions/ Issue: Can task copied to another projects?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: No but In pro version their is an option to assign multiple project to multiple task.

Questions/ Issue: Power BI integration in standard version?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: For Power BI integration you have to upgrade the app into pro version, we provide you custom solution to integrate it.

Questions/ Issue: Can we Submit timesheets without approval. ?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: In pro version their is a setting of direct approval, by this timesheet will not go to manager.

Questions/ Issue: Reporting doesn’t give summary for charged hours by projects?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: It is available in enterprise version of timesheet.

Questions/ Issue: Can we edit submitted timesheets ?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: Once the timesheet is approved by manager it can not be edit, an submitted timesheet can be edit before approval. Manager can reject it then the user can amend it and submit again.

Questions/ Issue: If the setting is enable for direct submission, can timesheet edit after submission.
Answer /Steps to Resolve: No, it is not possible to edit timesheet after submission.

Questions/ Issue: As an admin, I'm unable to delete the timesheet data from a particular employee. How can I delete the timesheet input from this particular employee to reset the timesheet for him/her without compromising the project, customer and tasks data already in the app?
Answer /Steps to Resolve:
There is two option is available to remove the existing timesheet data :

First You can remove the rejected, drafted and pending 
timesheet from employee portal and if the timesheet is approved, manager
 need to reject first then employee can remove the rejected timesheet.
Or second we can provide a list URL where timesheet data stored so you can delete timesheet from their.

Questions/ Issue: Can we have any extra custom feild in timesheet?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: In standard and pro version it is not possible but In enterprise version their is functionality to create custom feild.

Questions/ Issue: Can  employee add task and projects in timesheet ?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: In pro version their is a setting by enabling this employee can add only task in timesheet. Steps - Setting -> Project/Task ssetting -> select All users and save it.

Questions/ Issue: Once my trial is over, will I lose tasks/projects that I’ve imported using the PRO version? Or will the info remain and I just lose the PRO features?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: There will be no changes in data. Only the PRO version feature will revert back to the standard version.

Questions/ Issue: Can we see logs/ activity of users in timesheet?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: In timesheet logs generate only when user is performing any activity by grant permission option. We can see this from Logs option in Left Navigation.

Questions/ Issue: Can we upload documents in Timesheet App?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: Yes, their is an option of upload documents in left navigation.

Questions/ Issue: Can we assign project to specific employee?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: In Enterprise version of timesheet app their is the option of  Assign Project to employee in left nevigation, by this we can do this.

Questions/ Issue: Can we create super user like a super manager?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: Yes, In enterprise version of timesheet we can create super user, by super user option in left navigation.

Questions/ Issue: Is it possible to export data with daily information – export CSV only gives us weekly data
Answer /Steps to Resolve: The app is designed to generate weekly reports and this feature is not available out of the box in any version of the app. We can always customize this on top of the Enterprise version if that is a must needed feature for you.

Questions/ Issue: When we do export CSV – does it export all data based on filter or do we need to change the paging of the table from 25/50 to ALL?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: Yes, you will have to select “All” in page range so that you get to see all reports. Standard version has limitations on the export but as you are using Professional version already, it will allow you to export large reports in one click.

Questions/ Issue: Is it possible to enter to times on the timesheet in a ‘To’ and ‘From’/Start time and end time format?
Answer /Steps to Resolve: In the Pro application, this feature is not available. We can customize it based on your requirements.

Questions/ Issue: Is it possible to have a manager or a crew leader to enter the timesheet time for the crew members?
Answer /Steps to Resolve:
In the Pro app, the Grant Permission feature is available. Using that feature we can give authority of one user to another.  For more details please go through the below link.
